---

import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>

<body>
	<Header />

	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<h1>Hi, I'm Manubhav Sharma</h1>

			<p>
				Computer Science (AI) student building projects, exploring systems,
				and documenting everything I learn along the way.
			</p>

			<p>
				This blog is my digital notebook — a place for experiments,
				project breakdowns, technical notes, and lessons learned while
				building real-world applications.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>

			<p>
				I believe the fastest way to learn is to build publicly.
				Here I share concepts, mistakes, debugging journeys,
				and practical implementation details.
			</p>

			<ul>
				<li>Technical tutorials and explainers</li>
				<li>Project architecture breakdowns</li>
				<li>AI experiments and implementations</li>
				<li>Development notes and debugging stories</li>
				<li>System design learnings</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Things I Enjoy Building</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>AI-powered applications</li>
				<li>Full-stack web platforms</li>
				<li>Mobile applications</li>
				<li>Developer tools and productivity systems</li>
				<li>Automation workflows</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Current Focus</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>Deep Learning & Neural Networks</li>
				<li>Scalable System Design</li>
				<li>Data Structures & Algorithms</li>
				<li>Software Testing Methodologies</li>
				<li>Performance-focused engineering</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Projects I'm Proud Of</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>FIR Classification System using NLP and Deep Learning</li>
				<li>Collaborative Team Management Platform</li>
				<li>Bluetooth Data Streaming & Visualization App</li>
				<li>Expense Tracking Platform</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Why This Blog Exists</h2>

			<p>
				I created this space because documenting ideas forces me
				to understand them better.
			</p>

			<p>
				If a concept, project, bug, or experiment taught me something useful,
				there’s a good chance it will end up here.
			</p>

			<p>
				Learn. Build. Break things. Repeat.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</body>
```

</html>
